      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FUN DAY (1) flew the lids and led throughout to score last time at big odds, winning by 3.5 lengths at this track over 390m (22.10). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Can measure up again. UNIQUE ABILITY (7) was in winning form two back (19.75) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 8th. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Cannot be left out. LADY DREAMER (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Summer's Scrub (21.99) in a Grade 4. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can measure up. GOLDSTAR RODNEY (2) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
